{"tid":633381,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[NBA 2K18] LIHKG MyTeam盃 #1","createTime":"2018-04-18T09:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T13:48:46.000Z","uid":87988,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cdb0e42320f86b6c271fd1fe112ec0ce29657a95","tid":633381,"uid":87988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T09:10:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第一屆 LIHKG MyTeam盃</span><br />\n<br />\n召集所有打開NBA 2K既巴打<br />\n黎緊我地希望搞個MyTeam 1 on 1 既連登盃<br />\n希望多d 2k既玩家可以發掘下呢個mode<br />\n本身有玩開既巴打又可以一齊交流下 分享下相關資訊<br />\n<br />\n總之<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">比賽第一 友誼第二 誠意邀請各路高手用技術黎踐踏對手既尊嚴</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nmyteam專用tg group: <a href=\"https://t.me/nba2kmyteam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnba2kmyteam&d=tqRGKOaiWHhoCo5CzJ7%2Bzv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d481d884\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/nba2kmyteam</a><br />\n2K交流group: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/DgJ7GQ40LGRjc81kLFk2iA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FDgJ7GQ40LGRjc81kLFk2iA&d=tqRGKOaiWHhoCo5CzJ7%2Bzv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=1419745b\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/DgJ7GQ40LGRjc81kLFk2iA</a><br />\n<br />\n報名form: <a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/T1ePhbtrXwPTQdN73\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FT1ePhbtrXwPTQdN73&d=tqRGKOaiWHhoCo5CzJ7%2Bzv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d855949f\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/T1ePhbtrXwPTQdN73</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Tournament Rule:</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 今次會以淘汰賽形式進行, 會用free online source黎做分組抽籤,紀錄賽果等既管理<br />\n<br />\nsource url: <a href=\"http://www.online-brackets.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.online-brackets.com&d=tqRGKOaiWHhoCo5CzJ7%2Bzv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=eb8d8ad4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.online-brackets.com</a><br />\n玩家可以隨時係呢個網站查看賽程<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 隊伍陣容要求:<br />\n會用我地自訂Salary Cap既方式黎限制, 詳情如下<br />\n<br />\nSalary Cap: 6000<br />\n<br />\npink diamond: 1600<br />\ndiamond: 1200<br />\namethyst: 800<br />\nruby: 400<br />\nsapphire: 200 <br />\nemerald or below: will not be counted<br />\n<br />\np.s. 如果用過左salary cap既球隊黎玩, 對方有權決定該次結果是否用作計算<br />\n<br />\n3. 約戰及比賽方式<br />\n當online brackets入面既賽程表update後<br />\n大家需要同黎緊比賽既對手進行約戰<br />\nadd psn friend, 選好隊伍, 再係myteam mode開始打friendly<br />\n比賽結果由勝方tg send俾是旦一個admin, admin就會幫你係online brackets上面update資料<br />\n<br />\n4. 報名方式<br />\n以google form形式提供玩家資料, 包括psn ID及tg ID及tg<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/T1ePhbtrXwPTQdN73\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FT1ePhbtrXwPTQdN73&d=tqRGKOaiWHhoCo5CzJ7%2Bzv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d855949f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/T1ePhbtrXwPTQdN73</a><br />\n強烈建議入tg group, 有咩唔明可以即時問<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c287b63314e7b0f8cd92bd4b8ed40fa797917442","tid":633381,"uid":18327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T09:14:45.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c7201207bbf3587bbe46d09c49123eb0cb54d3c","tid":633381,"uid":18327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T13:06:40.000Z","msg":"無人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1002c0ed754d5c2ef81209bd2c5836c86f31e4d2","tid":633381,"uid":106683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c7201207bbf3587bbe46d09c49123eb0cb54d3c","tid":633381,"uid":18327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T13:06:40.000Z","msg":"無人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:37:06.000Z","msg":"Lag 機lag到 玩唔到<img src=\"